86
00:06:24.750 --> 00:06:28.830
It's written in blank verse
with an occasional rhyme.

87
00:06:32.070 --> 00:06:36.860
News, news has a kind of mystery when I
shook hands with Chou En-lai on this bare

88
00:06:36.860 --> 00:06:39.210
field outside Peking just now.

89
